🛒 Super Store Sales Dashboard

📌 Project Overview
This project showcases an interactive Sales Dashboard built using Power BI to analyze business performance and generate actionable insights. The dashboard provides a comprehensive view of sales, profit, customer behavior, and product performance.

🎯 Objective
To transform raw sales data into meaningful insights that help in:
Improving business decision-making
Identifying profitable segments
Understanding customer trends

📊 Key Metrics
💰 Total Sales: 1.57M+
📈 Total Profit: 175K+
📦 Total Quantity Sold: 22K+
👥 Total Customers: 773
🧾 Total Orders: 5901

📈 Dashboard Features
🔍 Region Filter – Analyze data across Central, East, South, and West
📅 Monthly Trends – Sales & profit comparison over time
🚚 Shipping Mode Analysis – Performance by delivery type
💳 Payment Mode Insights – COD, Online & Card distribution
🗂️ Category Analysis – Office Supplies, Technology, Furniture
📦 Sub-Category Breakdown – Identify top-selling products
🗺️ Geographical Visualization – Sales & profit by state

🛠️ Tools & Technologies
Power BI – Data visualization
DAX – Data calculations
Excel / CSV – Data source 

🔍 Key Insights
The West region shows strong sales performance
Technology category generates high revenue
Majority of orders are shipped via Standard Class
Certain months show peak sales indicating seasonal trends

📚 Learnings
Built interactive dashboards using Power BI
Applied DAX for calculated measures
Improved data storytelling & visualization skills

